features: 【Generously-sized and Comfortable Mesh Chair】- This office chair is designed with spaciousness in mind, making it larger than other mesh office chairs available. It is suitable for individuals with heights ranging from approximately 5'5" to 6'2". The desk task chair features a wide top backrest with a width of 19.29'', accommodating various body types comfortably. The seat dimensions measure 19.68''W x 19.68''D, with an adjustable height range of 19.29'' to 23.22''. The headrest dimensions are 13.38''W x 7.48''H. With a weight capacity of 300 pounds, this chair offers ample support for different users.

【Density Molded Foam Cushion】- Soft sponge cushions can strain the lower back, while firm cushions can impede blood flow. Our molded foam seat cushion is engineered with the perfect density. It provides a delicate balance of support and comfort, ensuring durability and long-lasting comfort even during extended periods of sitting.

【Ergonomic Office Chair】- Experience exceptional support with this ergonomic desk task chair that provides comprehensive support for the head, back, hips, hands, and lumbar region. Its adjustable seat height, lumbar support, headrest, and flip-up arms ensure a customized fit, catering to individual needs and enabling comfortable long-hour sitting.

【Flexible Headrest & Tilt Back】 - This computer chair features an adjustable headrest with a 4-inch height adjustment range and a 60-degree rotation angle. The backrest of the office task chair can be tilted between 90 and 135 degrees, with the option to lock it in 3 different positions. This provides you with the flexibility to customize the chair according to your preferences, whether you need optimal support for work or a comfortable position for relaxation.

【Flip-up Armrests & Coat Hanger】- The executive office chair is equipped with flip-up armrests, allowing you to easily slide the chair directly under your desk, thereby saving valuable space in your office area. Additionally, the chair features a practical coat hanger design at the back, providing a convenient place to hang your clothes or bags, helping to maintain a neat and tidy appearance in your workspace.

【5-Year Warranty】- We provide all the necessary tools in the package for easy and efficient assembly, allowing you to complete the installation process in just 25 minutes. Furthermore, this big and tall ergonomic gaming chair is backed by a 5-year warranty, offering you peace of mind and long-term protection.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Life Saver for Teacher with Back and Neck Pain
reviews.reviewText: This is the third chair I've purchased from this manufacturer. It is obvious that they listen to feedback from customers and make every effort to improve form and function. Apart from the cheerful colors, the big upgrades on this chair are the fully adjustable headrest, the thicker cushion, and the wider back. The coat rack will also be a useful feature for many people at the office. I am a piano teacher who sits for long periods of time, working with students. When I'm not teaching, I sit in my craft room for long periods. I have pinched nerves in my neck and lower back. I cannot overstate the importance of my chairs being as ergonomic as possible. This chair is ideal for me at 5'5", with the seat in the lowest position. The S curve fits my back perfectly, and the mesh is extremely comfortable. If needed, I can tweak the position of the padded/cushioned lumbar support with the built-in adjustment slider. The adjustable headrest makes such a difference to me. I can easily shift it if I need to relieve pressure on my neck. This is the chair you won't mind sitting in ALL day. I LOVE the color combinations, which are perfect for my little craft room. I can easily roll the chair from one workstation to another. The chair feels sturdy, and the quality is all top-notch. I believe it will last a long time. It was easy to put together. They included the necessary tools and even provided white gloves for handling the hydraulic lift. This is a fantastic chair for the price. The quality and value make it stand out from the rest. You can't go wrong with this one.

reviews.reviewText: Assembling it was a breeze – no hassle or frustration involved. The design really nails the balance between support and comfort. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exceeded my expectations!
reviews.reviewText: The build quality of this chair is great! The plastic has a nice weight to it, and the pink fabric is super soft (and a great color!) I also really like the vented back.The lumbar support really impressed me, as it is adjustable and stays in place. I also love the coat hanger attachment for the headrest.Construction was simple and only took about 30 minutes. I really liked the attention to detail, as the product also included screw covers to keep a nice, clean look. Instructions also came with gloves, which was very thoughtful!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars FOKESUN Ergonomic Office Chair
reviews.reviewText: The assembly took about 45 minutes - not too difficult. Instructions were OK, but no clear explanation of how to adjust the built in lumbar support although the existence of the lumbar support is mentioned on a picture. Chair seems sturdy and is very comfortable. There is some concern how the light colors will hold up in the long run. The spokes on the base are painted white, and sometimes I rest my feet there - already showing scuff marks - a rubber strip on top of the spokes would help.In sum it seems to be a sturdy and very comfortable chair at a reasonable price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The Perfect Gift...
reviews.reviewText: I got this chair for my wife as a gift. She's pretty picky about these kind of stuff, but this one really met our expectations. First off, it looks sleek and modern – the wide backrest and cool design give it a professional vibe. Plus, they added a coat hanger at the back, which she found really handy. The chair is not just about looks, though. The flip-up armrests are a cool move – you can easily slide it under the desk, saving space. The foam cushion is comfy without being too soft or too firm, perfect for long hours of sitting. My wife loved especially the adjustable lumbar support feature after the old one - it's great for back pain due to long work hours. Putting it together was pretty easy, took me around 20-25 minutes. And the 5-year warranty is a nice bonus for that extra peace of mind. In a nutshell, it's a mix of style, practicality, and comfort. My wife loved her new chair, and I'd definitely recommend it to anyone who wants a top-notch ergonomic chair without sacrificing style.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2023

reviews.reviewText: I ordered this chair for my daughter and she loves it. It was very easy to assemble - you don't have to put on the headrest if you don't want it. The seat is very comfortable. It moves and spins with ease. It is also easy to adjust up and down. No issues whatsoever. My daughter loves the pink color and the overall look of the chair.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect home office chair.
reviews.reviewText: This chair is super comfortable and works great in my office. The chair’s seat height can be adjusted easily, and the chair arms and head rest are also adjustable. Assembly was not too difficult either. Very happy with this chair!
